WEBVTT

00:00.000 --> 00:09.000
A co-founder speaks on camera in an office setting, introducing ComfyUI.

00:09.000 --> 00:19.500
The speaker explains the limitations of existing AI tools and Comfy's open source approach.

00:19.500 --> 00:36.500
Footage of the ComfyUI node-based interface, demonstrating how users combine model components visually.

00:36.500 --> 00:49.500
Examples of professional use cases: Hollywood studios, advertising agencies, and creative fields.

00:49.500 --> 01:02.000
Team members share their experience working at Comfy, highlighting the community and product connection.

01:02.000 --> 01:17.500
Engineers discuss the culture of ownership, driving product initiatives beyond assigned tasks.

01:17.500 --> 01:30.000
A designer describes the excitement of working on ComfyUI's frontier design challenges.

01:30.000 --> 01:38.500
Discussion of Comfy's transparent culture and open source code practices.

01:38.500 --> 01:56.000
A co-founder shares the mission: making open source win so everyone benefits.

01:56.000 --> 02:10.000
Closing message inviting talented people to join the team, with a group shot of the Comfy team.
